        <p>Pissed about SOPA, it will be back. Here are some better ways to keep it from coming back:</p>
<p>Make sure these pricks don&#39;t get reelected:</p>
<p>Lamar Smith (R-TX)  -- introduced the legislation
Harry Reid (D-NV) 
Howard Berman (D-CA) 
Marsha Blackburn (R-TN) 
Mary Bono Mack (R-CA) 
Steve Chabot (R-OH) 
John Conyers (D-MI) 
Ted Deutch (D-FL) 
Elton Gallegly (R-CA) 
Bob Goodlatte (R-VA) 
Timothy Griffin (R-AR) 
Dennis A. Ross (R-FL) 
Adam Schiff (D-CA) 
Lee Terry (R-NE) </p>
<p>And boycott these companies that supported the legislation:
